#~ msgid ""
#~ "`Kerning, in SVG 1.1 <https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/"
#~ "text.html#KerningProperty>`_ behaves slightly differently than ``font-"
#~ "kerning`` in CSS. Krita by default uses the ``auto`` property for this, "
#~ "which means it is on. To turn it off use ``kerning: 0;`` in the ``style`` "
#~ "section of the text. Any other numeric value will be added to current "
#~ "``letter-spacing``."
